bbs-server (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add SQLite persistence layer with federation-ready schema
  * Add runtime path contract (BBS_PACKAGING_MODE=linux-fhs for FHS paths)
  * Add admin debug endpoints for operational visibility
  * Add Linux FHS packaging profile with systemd support
  * Add federation infrastructure (outbox worker, mock registrar, dedupe)
  * Improve template and plugin discovery via resolved paths

